{"tid":1939703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國研究：武漢肺炎或令患者失去味覺和嗅覺","createTime":"2020-03-23T09:41:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T03:17:22.000Z","uid":28114,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"837ef54a11959674f73f1da14314e3827a421e6b","tid":1939703,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T09:41:12.000Z","msg":"失去味覺或嗅覺成 COVID-19 新病徵？英國耳鼻喉科專家研究發現<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2595000/2598101/20200323_doctor_01_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2595000%2F2598101%2F20200323_doctor_01_1024.jpg&h=0dcc2880&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前 <a href=\"http://ezone.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.hk&d=Eps995EZp4R4ibMzYmnfrwogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=0d1b6c9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ezone.hk</a> 報道，NBA 猶他爵士中鋒高拔為聯盟首位確診新冠肺炎的患者，而他近來交代病況時，更提到自己暫失嗅覺及味覺！原來，失去味覺或嗅覺可能是新冠肺炎的新病徵，只因英國耳鼻喉科協會 ENT UK 研究來自中、韓、意三國的新冠肺炎確診個案後，都發現患者有失去味覺或嗅覺的情況。<br />\n<br />\n英國耳鼻喉科協會 ENT UK 研究來自中、韓、意 3 國的新冠肺炎確診個案後，有重大發現<br />\n失去味覺或嗅覺或為感染新型冠狀病毒的症狀之一<br />\n喪失嗅覺或味覺的患者或成「隱性病毒帶菌者」<br />\n<br />\n英國 ENT UK 主席 Nirmal Kumar 與英國鼻科學會（British Rhinological Society）主席 Claire Hopkins 發布之聯合聲明提到，據中國、韓國、意大利的確診個案發現，新冠肺炎症狀可能包括喪失嗅覺或味覺，而這些患者沒有出現發燒、咳嗽等常見症狀，或成「隱性病毒帶菌者」也不自知。此外，聲明也提，正因英國、美國、法國和意大利北部的「無嗅覺症（Anosmia）」個案急增，因此這些患者可能仍為隱藏部分病毒的帶菌者，令新型冠狀病毒能迅速傳播。ENT UK 主席 Nirmal Kumar 稱，如新冠肺炎壓診患者是喪失嗅覺、味覺的話，意味病毒已經潛藏在鼻腔中。<br />\n<br />\n至於 ENT UK 另一名主要顧問教授也指，英國國家醫療服務 NHS 的兩名耳鼻喉科醫生就被他們的病人傳染新冠肺炎，現接受重症護理，且需要使用呼吸機輔助呼吸。初步估計兩位醫生都是在日常工作期間，被無症狀患者感染。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2598101?=B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2598101%3F%3DB&d=Eps995EZp4R4ibMzYmnfrwogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=ad4a2d94\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2598101?=B</a>"},{"pid":"2583d545d55d8085a869d777c33869bca62dda90","tid":1939703,"uid":28114,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T09:42:23.000Z","msg":"英國研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啫係信唔信佢好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb4a99cbce7303df7b7721cc0fb0539278c38c31","tid":1939703,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T09:45:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef5e8b7b49ef969e89adb82ba8a968330044077f","tid":1939703,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T09:45:41.000Z","msg":"以後可以瘋狂放屁"},{"pid":"855310c3e2e57c368f8b3d9cf804834199602bcc","tid":1939703,"uid":203058,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T09:46:32.000Z","msg":"唔使嘈龍門好唔好食了"},{"pid":"66a5daf4c8b65f2f9827ab868372941e4490d6d2","tid":1939703,"uid":50060,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T09:46:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aca648ce651480ff23d812254cf60c78536f810","tid":1939703,"uid":21917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T09:46:53.000Z","msg":"屌 沙加個招天舞寶輪咩"},{"pid":"711f593ebeeac453faf02c16fb4e89c1b36b5af3","tid":1939703,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2aca648ce651480ff23d812254cf60c78536f810","tid":1939703,"uid":21917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T09:46:53.000Z","msg":"屌 沙加個招天舞寶輪咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T09:47:46.000Z","msg":"唔該支持聯署，用選民壓力逼候選人「埋枱」參加初選/協調！<br />\n<br />\n【重開行動Post】立會要初選， 「三不投」聯署<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1935886\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1935886</a>"},{"pid":"bb48806d35f48491fb7720